So whether you live in an area with terrible
coverage, or just have a load of radio-blocking

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:59.320
materials, between you and your tower, remember
you’ve still got options to boost your network’s

00:05:59.320 --> 00:06:01.540
signal, and get your voice heard.

